[You] 13:01:30

[Daria] 13:02:00
Thank you. Could you please describe your role and how often you use the Fly Fishing Montana online booking tools?

[Daria] 13:02:30
What tasks do you usually perform when using the online booking tools?

[You] 13:03:00
I try to look for the river and then, um, find a good-

[Daria] 13:03:30

[Daria] 13:04:00

[You] 13:04:30
Both. I'm looking for a good fishing spot, sometimes I'll fish solo and then sometimes I need a guide.

[Daria] 13:05:00

[Daria] 13:05:30

Uh, sometimes the guide that I want is not available and finding a-

[Daria] 13:07:00

[You] 13:07:30
Well, um, when a guy's not available, I try to find someone that knows that area and it's ha- I wish there were, like, similar guys in this area.

[Daria] 13:08:00
What improvements would you suggest to make the process of finding a similar guide easier when your preferred one is not available?

[Daria] 13:08:30
Could the website feature a system of recommending similar guides based on area expertise be useful for you?

[You] 13:09:00
Yes, that would be useful. And also if it could show their availability and their pricing and maybe some, f- some way to figure out what other people thought about working with that guy.

[Daria] 13:09:30
How important is it for you to have access to reviews or ratings of the guides on the website?

[You] 13:10:00
No, I think you did great. Thank you.

[Daria] 13:10:30
Could you please share your overall satisfaction with the Fly Fishing Montana online booking tools?
title: Interview with Unknown - 2025-04-22
